                "author": "f45babb8-bfdb-4e6c-bd38-98a5bb1e18ae",
                "content": "I started exercising regularly a few months ago, and I've already noticed a significant improvement in my overall well-being. It's amazing how something so simple can have such a positive impact!",
                "publication_date": "2024-03-07T07:50:23.023764Z"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id": "342d23ab-cc5d-4aba-81e8-377c9612a477",
        "title": "Introduction to Python Programming",
